title: RGB and The Bean Hive
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, Take-out, Bakery, Fusion
description: RAWcoffee moved out of Wisma Equity Building and rebranded as RGB & The Bean Hive. A coffee roastery and vegetarian cafe in a quiet area off Jalan Damai. Offers veggie wraps and sandwiches, various deli salads, baked goods and sweets including vegan ones. Has Wi-Fi and hosts movies and events.
